## 8. Minimum Viable Product (MVP)

### MVP Scope: Single Vehicle, Voice-First Logging

**In Scope**
- User sign-up and authentication
- Create one vehicle/project
- Voice log entry (record → transcribe → save)
- View/search past logs
- Attach photos to logs
- Simple parts list with cost tracking
- Basic AI chat (context-aware Q&A about your project)
- Share one log entry as public post (no community feed yet)

**Out of Scope (Phase 2+)**
- Multiple vehicles/projects
- Video uploads
- Community feed / subscriptions
- Video auto-generation
- Collaborative projects
- Advanced analytics

### MVP Success Metrics

- **Adoption**: 500+ sign-ups in first month
- **Engagement**: 30%+ log in at least weekly
- **Retention**: 50%+ day-7 retention, 20%+ day-30 retention
- **Content**: 50+ voice log entries created
- **AI satisfaction**: 4.0+ star rating for AI chat feature

