## Appendix A: Glossary

- **Build Log**: A documented record of work done on a vehicle project
- **Build Post**: A published, shareable summary of a build project (can be generated from build logs)
- **Garage**: A user's collection of vehicle projects
- **Log Entry**: A single record in a build log (typically one per work session)
- **MVP**: Minimum viable product—the simplest version with core features
- **Premium Tier**: Paid subscription level with advanced features
- **RipEm**: The name of this platform/product

